'''波士頓兒童博物館'''（{{lang-en|Boston Children's Museum}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://zaubee.com/biz/boston-childrens-museum-0nursz8h |title=Boston Children's Museum |publisher=|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20220602102641/https://zaubee.com/biz/boston-childrens-museum-0nursz8h |archivedate=June 2, 2022}}</ref>）是位於[[美國|美國]][[麻薩諸塞州|麻薩諸塞州]][[波士頓|波士頓]]的一座[[兒童博物館|兒童博物館]]。

==历史==
创建于1913年，展示主題是兒童的教育。波士頓兒童博物館地處兒童碼頭，是美國第二座兒童博物館，提供眾多服務兒童的娛樂和教育活動<ref name=Brookline>Campbell, Karen. "Empowering Kids." ''Our Town Brookline''. March 2007: 6-9.</ref><ref name=Dodger>Palmer, Thomas C. Jr. [http://www.boston.com/news/local/massachusetts/articles/2006/03/13/dodgers_owner_donates_a_park_to_his_hometown/ "Dodger Owner Donates a Park to his Hometown."] {{Wayback|url=http://www.boston.com/news/local/massachusetts/articles/2006/03/13/dodgers_owner_donates_a_park_to_his_hometown/ |date=20160304001544 }} ''Boston Globe''. March 13, 2006. Accessed on May 2, 2008.</ref>。

